results.title: Ugly X-Mas Sweater Phone Case iPhone 6, 6 Plus, 5, 5C, 5S, Galaxy S4, S5, S6, Note 4
results.description:
If you would like this in a different color please put the request in the order notes:
Ex.
"White Ink" or "Purple Ink"

-High quality clear case
-Image designed for all case sizes
-Not pixelated
-Printed right onto phone case
-Scratch resistant design
-Made to order

Type Of Case we use:
- iPhone 6 Plus - 2 Piece Hard Plastic Clear Case
- iPhone 6 - 2 Piece Hard Plastic Clear Case
- iPhone 5 & 5s - 2 Piece or 1 Piece Clear Case ( Please specify in order notes )
- Galaxy Note 4 - 2 Piece Hard Plastic Case
- Galaxy S6 - 2 Piece Hard Plastic Case
- Galaxy S5 - 2 Piece Hard Plastic Case
- Galaxy S4 - 2 Piece Hard Plastic Case
- Galaxy S3 - 1 Piece Clear Silicone Case

Each two piece case fits snugly around the phone and has a lip over the front screen to add protection.

Each design is printed with the highest quality materials. The design is cured onto the case to feature a scratch resistant design which should last longer than other cases. We add an extra clear finish to the print to improve the life of the design and durability.

We offer custom designs with your graphic or if you would like us to design a case for you please message us and we can work out all the details.

All cases are ready to ship within 1-2 business days and may even leave our warehouse the same day. All designs are printed in house in our Southern California location.

If you have any questions feel free to contact us and let us know. :)
